markets.title: How many faithless electors will there be?
markets.rules_primary: If there are exactly 10 or more faithless electors tallied at the counting of electoral votes by Congress for the 2024 election, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: If an elector attempts to be faithless but has their vote voided or invalidated, or replaced, then that is not encompassed by the market. The market will be based solely on the number of faithless ballots cast and counted by Congress in early January following the election.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early after Congress tallies electoral votes.
